---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<!-- Logo -->
  <img src="/TheAIBLUF/The-AI-BLUF.jpg" alt="Logo" class="logo" />
			
			<p>
				Welcome to The AI BLUF, where we deliver the most important AI developments and practical tools that reduce time to market, increase quality, and streamline your decision-making. Each post is designed to give you actionable insights and essential takeaways—so you can stay informed and make impactful decisions, without wasting time.
			</p>
			<p>
				We'll help you stay ahead of the curve with concise AI insights and tools curated for busy executives. Get the Bottom Line Up Front (BLUF) and actionable takeaways to make informed decisions fast, without the noise.
			</p>
			<p>Here are a few ideas on how to get started with the template:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Concise & Actionable: Get the Bottom Line Up Front (BLUF) on AI developments with clear, actionable takeaways.</li>
				<li>Time-Saving: Stay informed in less time with executive-friendly updates that cut through the noise.</li>
				<li>Industry-Relevant: Focused on AI headlines and tools that matter for business leaders, technologists, and innovators.</li>
				<li>Strategic Insights: Gain valuable insights to help you make informed decisions and stay ahead of AI trends.</li>
				<li>Focus on Impact: Understand how AI tools can reduce time to market, increase quality, and streamline your business processes.</li>
				<li>Perfect for Busy Executives: Tailored for leaders who need to stay ahead but don’t have hours to spare.</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				Have fun! If you get stuck, remember to <a href="https://docs.astro.build/"
					>read the docs
				</a> or <a href="https://astro.build/chat">join us on Discord</a> to ask questions.
			</p>
			<p>
				Looking for a blog template with a bit more personality? Check out <a
					href="https://github.com/Charca/astro-blog-template"
					>astro-blog-template
				</a> by <a href="https://twitter.com/Charca">Maxi Ferreira</a>.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
